╬In memory of Jonray Luis Sanchez-Iglesias
1983 - 2015
A brave and inspirational son, husband, father and brother,
taken from us far too soon but will be in our hearts forever.
Jonray enjoyed this beautiful garden with his two daughters.
'Life gives you a gift every day and you have to
use it as best you can as it won't last forever'"¾
